#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.61"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.61:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.61:0.2"
msgid "7. Mahāvagga"
msgstr "7. The Great Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 61. Assutavāsutta → assutavantusuttaṃ (bj) | assutavato (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.61:0.3"
msgid "61. Assutavāsutta"
msgstr "61. Uneducated"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.94"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.61:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn12.61:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme …"
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. …"

#. VAR: cātumahābhūtikasmiṃ → cātummahābhūtikasmiṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn12.61:1.3"
msgid ""
"“assutavā, bhikkhave, puthujjano imasmiṃ cātumahābhūtikasmiṃ kāyasmiṃ "
"nibbindeyyapi virajjeyyapi vimucceyyapi."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when it comes to this body made up of the four primary "
"elements, an uneducated ordinary person might become disillusioned, "
"dispassionate, and freed."

msgctxt "sn12.61:1.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

#. VAR: Dissati, bhikkhave → dissati hi bhikkhave (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn12.61:1.5"
msgid ""
"Dissati, bhikkhave, imassa cātumahābhūtikassa kāyassa ācayopi apacayopi "
"ādānampi nikkhepanampi."
msgstr ""
"This body made up of the four primary elements is seen to accumulate and "
"disperse, to be taken up and laid to rest."

# Not sure why BB repeats “this body composed of the four great elements” in this sentence. It’s not in the Pali.
msgctxt "sn12.61:1.6"
msgid "Tasmā tatrāssutavā puthujjano nibbindeyyapi virajjeyyapi vimucceyyapi."
msgstr ""
"That’s why, when it comes to this body, an uneducated ordinary person might "
"become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.61:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vuccati cittaṃ itipi, mano itipi, viññāṇaṃ itipi, "
"tatrāssutavā puthujjano nālaṃ nibbindituṃ nālaṃ virajjituṃ nālaṃ vimuccituṃ."
msgstr ""
"But when it comes to that which is called ‘mind’ or ‘sentience’ or "
"‘consciousness’, an uneducated ordinary person is unable to become "
"disillusioned, dispassionate, or freed."

msgctxt "sn12.61:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn12.61:2.3"
msgid ""
"Dīgharattañhetaṃ, bhikkhave, assutavato puthujjanassa ajjhositaṃ mamāyitaṃ "
"parāmaṭṭhaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Because for a long time they’ve been attached to it, thought of it as their "
"own, and mistaken it:"

msgctxt "sn12.61:2.4"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ti."
msgstr "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self.’"

msgctxt "sn12.61:2.5"
msgid ""
"Tasmā tatrāssutavā puthujjano nālaṃ nibbindituṃ nālaṃ virajjituṃ nālaṃ "
"vimuccituṃ."
msgstr ""
"That’s why, when it comes to this mind, an uneducated ordinary person is "
"unable to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.95"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.61:3.1"
msgid ""
"Varaṃ, bhikkhave, assutavā puthujjano imaṃ cātumahābhūtikaṃ kāyaṃ attato "
"upagaccheyya, na tveva cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But an uneducated ordinary person would be better off taking this body made "
"up of the four primary elements to be their self, rather than the mind."

msgctxt "sn12.61:3.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn12.61:3.3"
msgid ""
"Dissatāyaṃ, bhikkhave, cātumahābhūtiko kāyo ekampi vassaṃ tiṭṭhamāno dvepi "
"vassāni tiṭṭhamāno tīṇipi vassāni tiṭṭhamāno cattāripi vassāni tiṭṭhamāno "
"pañcapi vassāni tiṭṭhamāno dasapi vassāni tiṭṭhamāno vīsatipi vassāni "
"tiṭṭhamāno tiṃsampi vassāni tiṭṭhamāno cattārīsampi vassāni tiṭṭhamāno "
"paññāsampi vassāni tiṭṭhamāno vassasatampi tiṭṭhamāno, bhiyyopi tiṭṭhamāno."
msgstr ""
"This body made up of the four primary elements is seen to last for a year, "
"or for two, three, four, five, ten, twenty, thirty, forty, fifty, or a "
"hundred years, or even longer."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.61:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vuccati cittaṃ itipi, mano itipi, viññāṇaṃ itipi, "
"taṃ rattiyā ca divasassa ca aññadeva uppajjati aññaṃ nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"But that which is called ‘mind’ or ‘sentience’ or ‘consciousness’ arises as "
"one thing and ceases as another all day and all night."

msgctxt "sn12.61:4.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, makkaṭo araññe pavane caramāno sākhaṃ gaṇhati, taṃ "
"muñcitvā aññaṃ gaṇhati, taṃ muñcitvā aññaṃ gaṇhati;"
msgstr ""
"It’s like a monkey moving through the forest. It grabs hold of one branch, "
"lets it go, and grabs another; then it lets that go and grabs yet another."

msgctxt "sn12.61:4.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, yamidaṃ vuccati cittaṃ itipi, mano itipi, viññāṇaṃ "
"itipi, taṃ rattiyā ca divasassa ca aññadeva uppajjati aññaṃ nirujjhati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, that which is called ‘mind’ or ‘sentience’ or "
"‘consciousness’ arises as one thing and ceases as another all day and all "
"night."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.61:5.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako paṭiccasamuppādaṃyeva sādhukaṃ yoniso "
"manasi karoti:"
msgstr ""
"In this case, a learned noble disciple carefully and properly attends to "
"dependent origination itself:"

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.2"
msgid "‘iti imasmiṃ sati idaṃ hoti, imassuppādā idaṃ uppajjati;"
msgstr "‘When this exists, that is; due to the arising of this, that arises."

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.3"
msgid "imasmiṃ asati idaṃ na hoti, imassa nirodhā idaṃ nirujjhati—"
msgstr ""
"When this doesn’t exist, that is not; due to the cessation of this, that "
"ceases. That is:"

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.4"
msgid "yadidaṃ avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "Ignorance is a condition for choices."

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.5"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. …"

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.6"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.7"
msgid "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho;"
msgstr ""
"When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease."

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.8"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.61:5.9"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’ti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.61:6.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi "
"nibbindati, saññāyapi nibbindati, saṅkhāresupi nibbindati, viññāṇasmimpi "
"nibbindati;"
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, "
"feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness."

msgctxt "sn12.61:6.2"
msgid ""
"nibbindaṃ virajjati, virāgā vimuccati, vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "sn12.61:6.3"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.61:6.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
